From: stopless-java-gc <noreply@anthropic.com>
Subject: Hook src/cap_runtime/ into the HotSpot build

This patch wires our out-of-tree cap_runtime static library into the
HotSpot libjvm link line, and exposes its public header via the
JVM build's include path. No HotSpot source changes beyond the build
system are made by this patch. Subsequent patches in patches/openjdk-jdk17/
add the actual ZGC modifications that consume the cap_runtime ABI.

Refs: docs/01_phase_i_zgc_port.md §4

